choice
    prompt "Used V4L-DVB source tree"
    default V4L_SRC_TBSDTV

    config V4L_SRC_TBSDTV
        bool "TBS"
        help
            TBS Technologies is a company which specializes in developing, manufacturing and marketing of
            digital TV tuner cards for PC. They maintain a fork of LinuxTV repo for their open source drivers.
            You want to use this if you have a device from TBS.

            Repo: https://github.com/tbsdtv/linux_media

    config V4L_SRC_LINUXTV
        bool "LinuxTV"
        help
            The LinuxTV community develops and maintains the Linux Kernel Media Subsystems.
            Use this if you are unsure.

            Repo: https://git.linuxtv.org/media_tree.git/

endchoice
